```plantuml
@startuml eProsima_FIWARE-SH
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #f0f0f0
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Integration Service" as IS

package "FIWARE System Handle" as FISH {
  rectangle "NGSIV2Connector" as Connector #lightblue
  rectangle "Listener" as Listener #lightyellow
  rectangle "Publisher" as Publisher #lightgreen
  rectangle "Subscriber" as Subscriber #lightpink
  rectangle "conversion.hpp" as Conversion #lightgray
}

rectangle "FIWARE Context Broker" as FCB #d9e7fd

IS --> Connector : Register SystemHandle
Connector --> Listener : Initialize
Connector --> Publisher : Create Publisher
Connector --> Subscriber : Create Subscriber
Listener -> FCB : Listen for notifications
Publisher -> FCB : Publish data
Subscriber -> FCB : Subscribe to data
FCB --> Listener : Send notifications
Listener --> Connector : Forward notifications
Publisher --> Connector : Convert data via Conversion
Subscriber --> Connector : Convert data via Conversion
Connector -> IS : Communicate data

@enduml
```